      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with no known major issues, and the interior remains clean, comfortable, and smoke-free. The exterior is in great shape overall, though it does show some minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with regular use. It serves as a reliable daily driver that has many miles of life left for its next owner.",
