    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers dependable transportation for its next owner. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car drives well, there are visible signs of wear including minor exterior scratches and some fading on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly and functional daily driver.",
