    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This specimen has been meticulously preserved, offering a showroom-quality finish that satisfies even the most discerning collector. From its flawless exterior to the untouched luxury of the cabin, every aspect of this car reflects peak mechanical and aesthetic standards. For those seeking an uncompromising driving experience in an investment-grade vehicle, this is the definitive choice.",
